json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token property\">\"homepage\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"http://[본인계정명].github.io/[생성한 레포명]\"</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>scripts 옵션 수정</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token property\">\"scripts\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">//...</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">\"predeploy\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"npm run build\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">\"deploy\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"gh-pages -d build\"</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>git init</li>\n<li>git에 레포지토리 주소 추가</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"cli\"><pre class=\"language-cli\"><code class=\"language-cli\">git remote add origin https://github.com/[본인계정명]/[레포지토리 명].git</code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"6\">\n<li>\n<p>아까 packge.json에 등록해놓은 명령어를 실행하여 배포하자.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"cli\"><pre class=\"language-cli\"><code class=\"language-cli\">npm run deploy</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>  <a href=\"https://github.com/gitname/react-gh-pages/tree/f7493337485ec85717a3bcd0fb732b13f5b0aada\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">react-gh-pages</a></p>","excerpt":"원래는.. build -> git init -> 깃허브 레포생성 -> gh-pages 브랜치생성 후 다시 커밋 -> push react-gh-pages를 사용해서 편하게 해보자 react프로젝트로 이동 깃허브에 새로운 레포지토리 생성 packge.j…","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/react-gh-pages/#%EC%9B%90%EB%9E%98%EB%8A%94\">원래는..</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/react-gh-pages/#react-gh-pages%EB%A5%BC-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%B4%EC%84%9C-%ED%8E%B8%ED%95%98%EA%B2%8C-%ED%95%B4%E